{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"forensic-adoring-kudu","description":"## What\nAdopt the B1 batch primitive on the NDJSON importer's independent passes so a bulk import\ncommits `ceil(events/chunk)` commits instead of one-per-event.\n\n## Why\n`src/rebar/_io/import_ndjson.py` already has idempotency-by-`source_id` and deferred-push,\nbut each pass still calls `rebar.create_ticket`/`edit_ticket`/`link`/`comment`, and each of\nthose flows `composer.create_core`/`_commands/_seam.py::append_event` ->\n`event_append.write_and_push` (one lock + one commit per call). That per-event seam is the\nreal bottleneck. Routing the independent passes through B1's `batch_stage_and_commit`\ncollapses their commits.\n\n## Scope\n- Add a compose-ONLY seam: a variant of `create_core`/`append_event` that RETURNS the\n  composed `(ticket_id, event_dict)` WITHOUT committing (`src/rebar/_commands/composer.py`,\n  `src/rebar/_commands/_seam.py`).\n- In `src/rebar/_io/import_ndjson.py`, buffer composed events per pass and flush through\n  `batch_stage_and_commit` in chunks (default 256, hard-coded — no new config key).\n- Independent passes only: Pass 1 (CREATE) and Passes 2a–2d (parents/links/file-impact/\n  comments). Pass 2e (statuses) is STATEFUL (children-before-parents, `cascade=False`) →\n  left per-event.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Compose-only seam returns `(ticket_id, event_dict)` without committing; the existing committing path is unchanged for all other callers\n- [ ] Importer Passes 1 + 2a–2d buffer composed events and flush via `batch_stage_and_commit` in 256-event chunks\n- [ ] Pass 2e (statuses) remains per-event (stateful ordering preserved)\n- [ ] A real import run produces the same final replayed state as the per-event path (byte/state parity) with far fewer commits\n- [ ] Idempotent re-import (source_id re-scan) still skips already-imported events\n- [ ] `make lint && make typecheck && make test` all green","id":"6386-fa1d-d6b5-49ae","parent_id":"ce4c-f963-363b-44b6","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"B2: route the NDJSON importer's independent passes through the batch primitive"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783649385225761001,"uuid":"b691d713-2ff8-405c-8dca-24355cb5c40c"}